{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"EventTarget()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/EventTarget","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><em><code>EventTarget()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\"><code>addEventListener()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/dispatchEvent\"><code>dispatchEvent()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/removeEventListener\"><code>removeEventListener()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":null,"id":null,"isH3":false,"query":"api.EventTarget.EventTarget","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/EventTarget/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><code><strong>EventTarget()</strong></code>&nbsp;构造方法将会创建一个新的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a> 对象实例。</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">var <var>myEventTarget</var> = new EventTarget();</pre>\n\n\n\n<p>无。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a> 实例。</p>\n\n\n\n<pre id=\"ct-20\" class=\"notranslate\">class MyEventTarget extends EventTarget {\n  constructor(mySecret) {\n&nbsp;   super();\n    this._secret = mySecret;\n  }\n\n  get secret() { return this._secret; }\n};\n\nlet myEventTarget = new MyEventTarget(5);\nlet value = myEventTarget.secret;  // == 5\nmyEventTarget.addEventListener(\"foo\", function(e) {\n  this._secret = e.detail;\n});\n\nlet event = new CustomEvent(\"foo\", { detail: 7 });\nmyEventTarget.dispatchEvent(event);\nlet newValue = myEventTarget.secret; // == 7</pre>\n\n\n\n<table>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-eventtarget-eventtarget\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">EventTarget() constructor</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n\n<p>The compatibility table on this page is generated from structured data. If you'd like to contribute to the data, please check out <a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data</a> and send us a pull request.</p>\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"EventTarget() 构造方法将会创建一个新的EventTarget 对象实例。","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"EventTarget()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"EventTarget()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"EventTarget()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"EventTarget()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"EventTarget()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"EventTarget()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/eventtarget/eventtarget","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/eventtarget/eventtarget/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget","title":"EventTarget"},{"uri